dcat-dataset-strings.description:
This is a collection of the raw and processed data for the ground-based time-domain electromagnetic (TEM) data for a survey conducted by CSIRO Land and Water on behalf of BESIK in October 2014.  This collection consists of the raw and processed TEM data for the survey conducted near Liquica, Timor-Leste.  Please see CSIRO report:
Davis, AC and Ley-Cooper, AY, 2015. Ground-based time-domain electromagnetic soundings along river transects near Liquiçá, Timor-Leste. CSIRO: Land and Water Flagship Technical Report (EP-15-25-70).
